# Native addon binaries — rebuilt on-demand via `zig build native-addon`.
# Tracked-in-git addons silently drifted vs source (tb-alignment.md 7a).
# focus_exe.step.dependOn(native_addon_step) in build.zig auto-rebuilds;
# any other consumer must run `zig build native-addon` first.
packages/ts/native/dist/**/shm.node

